WEBVTT

00:00:01.024 --> 00:00:02.866
Tangu nilipokulia Kenya,

00:00:02.890 --> 00:00:05.441
nilijua nilitaka kusoma biokemia.

00:00:07.088 --> 00:00:12.619
Unaona, nilishuhudia madhara ya magonjwa kama malaria,

00:00:12.643 --> 00:00:15.336
na nilitaka kutafuta dawa ya kutibu wagonjwa.

00:00:15.765 --> 00:00:17.150
Hivyo nilijituma kwa bidii,

00:00:17.174 --> 00:00:20.961
nikapata udhamini kutoka Marekani, 
ambapo nilikuwa mtafiti wa kansa

00:00:20.985 --> 00:00:22.214
na nilipenda kazi yangu.

00:00:22.612 --> 00:00:24.699
Kwa mtu anayetaka kutibu magonjwa,

00:00:24.723 --> 00:00:26.434
hakuna wito mkubwa zaidi.

00:00:27.321 --> 00:00:30.673
Miaka kumi baadaye, nilirudi
Kenya kwa kufanya hilo tu.